<p> Here you can search a developer according to name,surname,email,city and age. If you need to search for a dev with a particular skill level, go back and click on: Search Developer With Skills </p>

<%= form_tag("/dev_results", method: "get") do %>
  <%= label_tag(:q, "Name: ") %>
  <%= text_field_tag(:q) %>
  <%= submit_tag("Search by Name") %>
<% end %>

